data.title: 124x signed F1 photos, Rosberg, Surtees, Trulli, Coulthard and many more – Racingexclusives
data.text:
This is a large set of signed photo’s and driver cards.

All photos are hand signed by the drivers themselves. Mostly Formula 1 drivers, some Sportscars, Le Mans and Indycar drivers, from the 1960 era untill the late 2010’s.

Great offer to start or expand your signed F1-collection.

Some of the drivers in this set are:

John Surtees, Nico Rosberg, Jarno Trulli, David Coulthard, Heins Harald Frentzen, Christian Klien, Pedro Diniz, Derek Bell, Tim Schenken, Pedro Lamy, Nick Heidfeld, Bruno Giacomelli, Tedyy Pilette, Scott Speed, Geoff Lees, Hideki Noda, Mika Salo, Christian Danner, Rene Arnoux, Vern Schuppen.

Due to the large number of photo’s no individual CoA will be issued, but all photo’s are hand signed and authentic.
